Abuja – A young Nigerian boy,  identified as Mr. Isaac Terkende has been reported dead after allegedly snapping a picture in a coffin. The young boy was reported to have died twenty-four hours after he had snapped the picture. Another Facebook user identified as James Igbudu took to his Facebook wall to share this piece of information when he shared a photo of Mr. Isaac in the coffin and his obituary. The photo showed him smiling in a coffin which he took just before he died. See The Photo Here: Source